rtmom is a client for "Remember the Milk" (http://www.rememberthemilk.com/). It is based on Elementary.

To install rtmom, run 

<pre>
opkg install rtmom
</pre>

Also see wiki (http://wiki.github.com/kichkasch/rtmom/end-user) for installation and usage instruction.

